<!-- Masthead-->
<div class="p-5 text-center bg-image"
    style=" background-image: url('/public/images/headerStock.jpg'); background-size: 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat">
<header class="masthead">
    
    <div class="container position-relative">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="text-center text-white">
                    <!-- Page heading-->
                    <h1 class="mb-5">Get started on your fitness journey today!</h1>
                    {{#if authenticated}}
                    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/profile" role="button">Go to your nutrition profile!</a>
                     {{else}}
                    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login" role="button">Click here to signup or login!</a>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
</div>
            
<!-- Icons Grid-->
<section class="features-icons bg-light text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="features-icons-item mx-auto mb-5 mb-lg-0 mb-lg-3">
                    <div class="features-icons-icon d-flex"><i class="bi-window m-auto text-primary"></i></div>
                    <h3>Easy to Use</h3>
                    <p class="lead mb-0">Our simple food and exercise log interface makes tracking your goals painless!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="features-icons-item mx-auto mb-5 mb-lg-0 mb-lg-3">
                    <div class="features-icons-icon d-flex"><i class="bi-layers m-auto text-primary"></i></div>
                    <h3>Smart Nutriton</h3>
                    <p class="lead mb-0">Your nutrtion profile will be custom tailored specifially to suit your needs! </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="features-icons-item mx-auto mb-0 mb-lg-3">
                    <div class="features-icons-icon d-flex"><i class="bi-terminal m-auto text-primary"></i></div>
                    <h3>Engage With Others</h3>
                    <p class="lead mb-0">The FitnessFluent community is widely accessible at our discussion forum!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<!-- Image Showcases-->
<section class="showcase">
    <div class="container-fluid p-0">
        <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('/public/images/stockFood.jpg')"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h2>Food Log</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-0">Every user has their own unique digital food journal. Here, you can enter the foods you ate on a particular
        day, along with the number of calories they contained. This will provide you with an easy way to keep
        track of your daily caloric requirements for your weight gain or weight loss goals. In addition, our 
        FoodSmart reccomendation system will reccomend foods to you based upon the number of calories you 
        have remaining on a particular day! </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col-lg-6 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('/public/images/fitnessStock.jpg')"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h2>Exercise Log</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-0">In addition to the capbility to log your daily food consumption, you will also have your own personal
        exercise log. Here, you can enter all of the different exercises you completed in a particular day, and 
        the number of calories you burned. When you enter exercise calories, it adjusts your daily caloric intake,
        allowing you to eat more food and still meet your goals!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('/public/images/stockStats.jpg')"></div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
                <h2>Visualize Progress Statistics</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-0">Sometimes, its' hard to appreciate how far you've come when working towards a long term goal. That's why
        FitnessFluent offers a progress page, where you can see a long term statistical display of your weight gain
        or weight loss journey. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
